Now then, let's call the Lui-tomos... Oh, wait...

373
00:35:21,105 --> 00:35:24,105
大丈夫？ なんか盛り上がってる？ ルイ友さん、大丈夫？
Are you guys okay? Are you excited? Lui-tomos, you all right?

374
00:35:26,605 --> 00:35:27,605
あ、ルイ友さんもね、座りたいか？
Oh, do you Lui-tomos want to sit down too?

375
00:35:28,205 --> 00:35:31,005
じゃ、ちょっと座る？ お膝に座ろうか。
Then, want to sit? How about sitting on my lap?

376
00:35:32,505 --> 00:35:33,905
最初に関...
First, I'll...

377
00:35:34,605 --> 00:35:35,605
