409
00:37:49,405 --> 00:37:50,905
痛いか？
Does it hurt?

410
00:37:51,305 --> 00:37:54,105
さっきはよくももみもみしやがって。おい！
How dare you keep rubbing me like that! Hey!

411
00:37:54,405 --> 00:37:57,005
えい！ えい！ えい！
Take that! And that! And that!

